{"tid":981312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"房署換晾衫架又唔啱用燒4億做場SHOW","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T13:05:12.000Z","uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"382afc559a8359d3262e8f2eb89f9c818b5a7926","tid":981312,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"房屋署使錢亂做，晾衫架愈換愈差，安全更成疑！房署耗資近<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">四億元</span></strong></span>為卅萬公屋戶額外加裝雙杆式晾衫架，首批屋邨已更換完畢，但大批居民批評新安裝的晾衫架新不如舊，設計、質量存在五宗罪，其中最離譜的是部分晾衫架安裝一星期便出現疑似銹迹，而且晾在架上的衣物容易吹落街，甚為困擾居民。有驗樓師指晾衫架短時間內出現銹迹及銹斑，質素成疑，亦會影響耐用性，接駁位一旦出現嚴重銹蝕更會增加鬆脫風險。<br />\n<br />\nttp://<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190114/mobile/odn-20190114-0114_00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190114%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190114-0114_00174_001.html&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2BbciszviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4b22d06d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190114/mobile/odn-20190114-0114_00174_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bac2b8bed088f39597e441ea61f0865775bc2388","tid":981312,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"$1xxx蚊連裝好似又ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c38566d423f2f8cad4045272f08fc6a6e6f539e","tid":981312,"uid":74897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:25:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c94e24c0cbe35ab0392b6a0887884192081f76","tid":981312,"uid":173162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"早兩日裝完<br />\n冇用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbe74a4049303fda0080333729d542078dea592","tid":981312,"uid":7206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"咁快生銹<img src